
  //////////////////////////////////////
    Usurper 0.19 - Upgrade Information 
  //////////////////////////////////////

1. you are upgrading from 0.18
2. you are upgrading from 0.17
3. you are upgrading from a pre 0.17 version

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
(1) Upgrading from v0.18
    unzip the archive in your usurper directory (overwrite all existing
    files).
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
(2) Upgrading from v0.17
    unzip the archive in your usurper directory (overwrite all existing
    files). run the 017to018.EXE program.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------
(3) Upgrading from a version below v0.17
    Download Usurper 0.18 version. In this archive you will find appropriate
    converters for older versions.
